Description: =====
        django-contenttype-tag
        =====
        
        It's easy app for get content type of instance at templates
        
        =====
        How to use
        =====
        
        1. Add 'generic_ct_tag' at INSTALLED_APPS::
        
              INSTALLED_APPS = (
                    ...
                    'generic_ct_tag',
              )
        
        3. At template::
        
              {% load generic_ct %}
        
              {% content_type obj as ct %}
              {{ ct.app_label }}
              {{ ct.model }}
        
              {# or #}
        
              {% content_type obj %} {# The resulr: <app_label>.<model> #}
        
